      <title>奥本海默称利率应该下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/oppenheimer-says-interest-rates-should-be-coming-down-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席全球股票策略师彼得·奥本海默 (Peter Oppenheimer) 谈论了美国货币政策的走向、股市在此次降息周期中的表现、市场回报为何应该扩大以及即将上任的特朗普政府提高关税将如何影响市场。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/oppenheimer-says-interest-rates-should-be-coming-down-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:17:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
