      <title>叙利亚因工人放弃机场而失去剩余的航空连接</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/syria-loses-remaining-air-connections-as-workers-abandon-airport</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴沙尔·阿萨德政权垮台后，叙利亚主要机场暂停运营，过去十年来一直保持低水平国际连通性的少数航班也停飞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/syria-loses-remaining-air-connections-as-workers-abandon-airport</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业借比特币浪潮通过可转换债券筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/firms-ride-bitcoin-wave-to-raise-billions-from-convertible-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择了一位对加密货币友好的金融家担任美国最高金融监管机构主席，加密货币的上涨使得该领域的少数几家公司成为赢家，这些公司效仿了微策略公司 (MicroStrategy Inc.) 出售可转换债券的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/firms-ride-bitcoin-wave-to-raise-billions-from-convertible-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:06:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
